    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086590/extras/b39f45553eed7efe47bdf8e29b26f188.poster.avif?t=1765794495\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086590/extras/b39f45553eed7efe47bdf8e29b26f188.webm?t=1765794495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086590/extras/b39f45553eed7efe47bdf8e29b26f188.mp4?t=1765794495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个后末日的黑暗奇幻世界里，诸神已经殒没。本游戏融合了撤离与动作角色扮演要素，挑战玩家恢复各个破碎领域的平衡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在死神的招募下，你将进入危险的地图，完成目标，对抗敌人和其他玩家，并获取战利品。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086590/extras/22d0e169fb2d7b3d9b57c1cda5a1cfe5.poster.avif?t=1765794495\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086590/extras/22d0e169fb2d7b3d9b57c1cda5a1cfe5.webm?t=1765794495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086590/extras/22d0e169fb2d7b3d9b57c1cda5a1cfe5.mp4?t=1765794495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在漫游神话国度，第一站是北欧神话。对付难缠的敌人，接受任务，收集强力装备和神器。掌握不同的游玩风格。本游戏环境公平，且有严格的反作弊工具。 <br><br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086590/extras/3999081d89d1c86943cbcd45b7c5ca78.poster.avif?t=1765794495\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086590/extras/3999081d89d1c86943cbcd45b7c5ca78.webm?t=1765794495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086590/extras/3999081d89d1c86943cbcd45b7c5ca78.mp4?t=1765794495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开局你身处自己的隐藏堡垒。在这里，你可以升级基地、自定义武装并准备战斗。每张地图都有独特的目标和财宝，但风险很高：死亡意味着失去一切，而成功撤离可以保留战利品。未来更新会加入新地图、玩家间交易和为不同游玩风格准备的额外模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086590/extras/ad3347edf8bfd0e6fa1d6105ac8e791f.poster.avif?t=1765794495\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086590/extras/ad3347edf8bfd0e6fa1d6105ac8e791f.webm?t=1765794495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086590/extras/ad3347edf8bfd0e6fa1d6105ac8e791f.mp4?t=1765794495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了高风险的死神vs死神vs环境的撤离模式外，还有别的游玩方式。单人剧情模式让你按自己的步调揭开众神殒没之谜，且没有丢失装备的风险。也可以选择PvE合作模式，与其他玩家组队，对抗各个派系，进一步了解剧情。未来推出的更新会加入合作模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086590/extras/0582b01fd4c7616ef03f50e8572b2a63.poster.avif?t=1765794495\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086590/extras/0582b01fd4c7616ef03f50e8572b2a63.webm?t=1765794495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086590/extras/0582b01fd4c7616ef03f50e8572b2a63.mp4?t=1765794495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们心系玩家，致力于让玩家社区来主导开发过程，并认真听取玩家们的真实心声。Alpha封测玩家将帮助我们改善游戏并塑造游戏未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想要参与吗？加入我们的Discord以了解最新动态，并说出你的想法。</p>",
